  <para>This is a comprehensive list and description of all of the
        <application>Hybrid 7</application> numerics that can be generated
        by the server.  This document is designed for client and script
        writers, to provide an easier way to get this information than having
        to read the source code themselves.</para>

  <para>All numerics are of the form <command>:<replaceable>originating.server
        numeric user parameters</replaceable></command>.  The parameters are
        described after listing the numerics.  Words in all capital letters
        are items that the server will insert text.  All substitutions are
        listed in order.  The default text is not listed, as it is easily (and
        often) changed.  If a <emphasis>:</emphasis> is listed in the text, it
        is sent explicitly by the server.</para>

